What you need to know:

The July 17 showpiece of African club football could feature a local side as Wydad Casablanca appear the strongest team in one half of the knockout drawThe July 10 final of the Caf Confederation Cup -- the African equivalent of the UEFA Europa League -- will be staged in Cotonou, the commercial capital of BeninEgypt was selected to host the first eight-team Caf Women's Champions League tournament during the second half of this year on dates to be announced